<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Nueva Solicitud de Viáticos</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .expense-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .actions {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .approve-button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .approve-button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .reject-button {
            background-color: #ff6b6b;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;
        }
        .reject-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff5252;
        }
        .comment-instructions {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
        }
        td {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Nueva Solicitud de Viáticos</h2>
        <p><strong>Solicitante:</strong> {{requestedBy}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>Información General</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Empresa:</strong> {{company}}</li>
                <li><strong>Sucursal:</strong> {{branch}}</li>
                <li><strong>Área:</strong> {{area}}</li>
                <li><strong>Motivo del Viaje:</strong> {{travelReason}}</li>
                <li><strong>Fecha de Salida:</strong> {{departureDate}}</li>
                <li><strong>Fecha de Regreso:</strong> {{returnDate}}</li>
                <li><strong>Fecha de Dispersión:</strong> {{disbursementDate}}</li>
                <li><strong>Monto Total:</strong> {{totalAmount}}</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>Detalles de Gastos</h3>
            <div class="expense-details">
                {{#each details}}
                <p><strong>{{concept}}:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>Objetivos del Viaje</h3>
            <p>{{travelObjectives}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="comment-instructions">
            <p><strong>Instrucciones:</strong> Seleccione una de las siguientes opciones para aprobar o rechazar la solicitud:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px; text-align: center;">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Aprobar:</strong></p>
                        <a href="{{apiUrl}}/expense-requests/{{requestId}}/approve?approverId={{approverId}}&comment=Aprobado" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                            Aprobar sin comentarios
                        </a><br>
                        <a href="{{apiUrl}}/expense-requests/{{requestId}}/approve?approverId={{approverId}}&comment=Aprobado.%20Favor%20de%20entregar%20comprobantes%20originales" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
                            Aprobar con comprobantes
                        </a>
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding: 10px; text-align: center;">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Rechazar:</strong></p>
                        <a href="{{apiUrl}}/expense-requests/{{requestId}}/reject?approverId={{approverId}}&comment=Rechazado.%20Falta%20información" style="background-color: #ff6b6b; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                            Rechazar - Falta información
                        </a><br>
                        <a href="{{apiUrl}}/expense-requests/{{requestId}}/reject?approverId={{approverId}}&comment=Rechazado.%20Montos%20incorrectos" style="background-color: #ff6b6b; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
                            Rechazar - Montos incorrectos
                        </a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Esta solicitud requiere su revisión y aprobación.</p>
        <p>Portal Grupo FG - Sistema de Viáticos</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 